s837: Four. Third month geng wu, General Guang passes away.
s838: Second month ding mao, Attendant in Emperor's Presence, Commandant Huo Yu becomes Right General.
s842: Establishes Crown Prince. Fifth month jia shen, honors elders, grants gold one hundred jin.
s843: Sixth month ren chen, Imperial Secretary Wei Xiang becomes Chancellor, sealed as Gao Ping Hou.
s844: Seventh month, An Shi becomes Grand Commandant, Guard General. Yu becomes Grand Commandant.
s849: Two. Seventh month ren yin, Yu waist cut.
s873: Six. Eighth month bing yin, An Shi passes away.
s878: Emperor suburban sacrifices Ganquan Supreme Altar, Fen Yin Hou Tu.
s880: Fourth month, Le Cheng Hou Xu Yan Shou becomes Strong Crossbow General. Rear General Chong Guo strikes Qiang. Jiuquan governor Xin Wu Xian becomes Breaking Qiang General. Han Zeng becomes Grand Commandant, Chariot Cavalry General.
s884: Emperor suburban sacrifices Yong five altars. Fen Yin produces precious jade ritual vessels.
s891: Fourth month wu xu, Imperial Secretary Bing Ji becomes Chancellor, sealed as Bo Yang Hou.
